main event: An unidentified object was spotted in the sky over Manchester, New Hampshire on July 25, 1967.
interesting points: The object appeared to be a reconnaissance-type aircraft and was observed for approximately 15 minutes.
The object was described as hovering and then disappearing to the east of Manchester.
The object was compared in brightness to a star, but was brighter.
The edges of the object were reported as fuzzy or blurred.
The object changed brightness and appeared to disappear and reappear.
